                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="19587" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Wed, 13 Sep 2006 09:57:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for pointing this out! WebSphere 6.1 seems to use a special &quot;bundleresource:&quot; URL there, which our PathMatchingResourcePatternResolver tries to resolve in the file system but cannot... I&apos;ve refined the implementation to simply ignore this and proceed with all other classpath roots instead of failing with an exception at that point.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Feel free to give this a try with the upcoming 2.0 RC4 release (or one of the next nightly snapshots)...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
